ition: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Despite investing in Rose back in 2017 and recognising its advancements, Neuner has decided not to pursue this narrative actively. According to the former CNBC analyst there is an abundance of other investment narratives in the market, such as gaming, and says this is why he is not championing or heavily investing in the Rose narrative at this time.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; padding: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: rgb(229, 232, 236) 0px 0px 10px;\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://lh7-us.googleusercontent.com/VZDkEKvebbQ6nWhZ5VCrQ-oK-JeWIISSgQ0xPt6-GwQ5RfVpTRaT7AEgfVRvLgzPvHdiyq8N8vU_CDfZssqiMV4faUpA0JUlreRAg6E78HIVjK1ffE86S1sfIC9aa7NpHl4mr1OnUKJqKEmZXQYZP4k\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://lh7-us.googleusercontent.com/VZDkEKvebbQ6nWhZ5VCrQ-oK-JeWIISSgQ0xPt6-GwQ5RfVpTRaT7AEgfVRvLgzPvHdiyq8N8vU_CDfZssqiMV4faUpA0JUlreRAg6E78HIVjK1ffE86S1sfIC9aa7NpHl4mr1OnUKJqKEmZXQYZP4k\" class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"font: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; display: block;\"></figure><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Source: Crypto Banter/ YouTube</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-liquid-staking-more-to-banter-s-liking\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 28px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Liquid Staking More to Banter’s Liking</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Eigenlayer is the talk of the town right now and Neuner<a href=\"https://cryptonews.com.au/news/milkyway-brings-liquid-staking-to-celestia-tia-115560/\" style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(81, 0, 252);\">&nbsp;is enthusiastic about the narrative of liquid staking</a>, particularly with regard to Eigenlayer. Eigenlayer is a protocol that enhances the concept of liquid staking. In traditional staking, users lock up their crypto, such as<a href=\"https://cryptonews.com.au/price/ethereum/\" style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(81, 0, 252);\">&nbsp;Ether (ETH)</a>, to support the operation and security of a blockchain network, earning rewards in return. However, their assets become illiquid during this period.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"https://cryptonews.com.au/news/miles-deutscher-unveils-key-narratives-behind-the-next-major-crypto-bull-run-117282/\" style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(81, 0, 252);\">Liquid staking, in contrast,</a>&nbsp;allows users to stake their crypto and receive a liquid token in return. This token represents their staked assets and can be used in other parts of the crypto ecosystem while still earning staking rewards. Essentially, it enables users to retain liquidity and engage in other investment opportunities without sacrificing their staking rewards.</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-eigenlayer-is-good-but-it-gets-better-says-neuner\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 28px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Eigenlayer is Good But It Gets Better, Says Neuner</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Neuner then says to his followers that he found a very promising project with a great risk-reward ratio.</p><div id=\"blockquote-block_c709522cdc42ace14def660b57f56842\" class=\"blockquote-container variant-personal\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin: 16px 0px 32px; padding: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); border-radius: 8px;\"><div class=\"blockquote-text\" style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 68px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative;\"><p style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">“I started speaking about STRIDE over here in December. To be fair, [since] November/ December STRIDE is already up 400%. But I still think that if you understand what I’m about to say to you, you will understand why I’m so bullish about this.”</span></p></div><div class=\"blockquote-attribution\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 68px; vertical-align: baseline; align-items: center; display: flex; gap: 10px;\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://cdn.cryptonews.com.au/2024/01/16202149/RAN-NEUNER.jpg\" class=\"author-image lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://cdn.cryptonews.com.au/2024/01/16202149/RAN-NEUNER.jpg\" style=\"font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 40px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 50%; width: 40px;\">Ran Neuner</div></div><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Neuner sees STRIDE as a unique investment opportunity due to its ability to offer optionality and exposure to an entire ecosystem rather than being reliant on the success of a single blockchain. This approach to liquid staking presents a potentially lower risk with diversified rewards, making it an attractive option for investors looking for exposure to the Cosmos network.</p><div id=\"blockquote-block_c37a46603079421dc85b697a48b9b602\" class=\"blockquote-container variant-personal\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin: 16px 0px 32px; padding: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); border-radius: 8px;\"><div class=\"blockquote-text\" style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 68px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative;\"><p style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">“The reason why STRIDE is different is because STRIDE is not a bet on just one chain, like Jito is on Solana or Lido is on ETH. STRIDE represents optionality on the success of any, many, or all Cosmos chains. Because Cosmos is a technology, STRIDE allows you to restake not only on one chain. Currently, it allows you to stake a few Cosmos chains, but soon, probably every single Cosmos chain. This means that when you invest in STRIDE, you’re betting that chains like Injective, Celestia, Zeta, or any other in the ecosystem will succeed.”</p></div><div class=\"blockquote-attribution\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 68px; vertical-align: baseline; align-items: center; display: flex; gap: 10px;\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://cdn.cryptonews.com.au/2024/01/16202149/RAN-NEUNER.jpg\" class=\"author-image ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://cdn.cryptonews.com.au/2024/01/16202149/RAN-NEUNER.jpg\" style=\"font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 40px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 50%; width: 40px;\">Ran Neuner</div></div>', '2024-11-07 09:36:43', '2024-11-07 09:55:09', 1, 'Next-Bull-Run:-These-Cryptos-Can-Deliver-Explosive-Returns', '262a888b2c8c4702d61a90b79b044122.png');

