(7, 'What is Dorado? How Dorado works?', 17, 21, '<p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">What is Dorado?<br style=\"border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"></strong><br style=\"border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">Dorado is a platform focused on offering a user-friendly platform for efficient staking and restaking on the Arbitrum network. It empowers users to optimize their earnings by providing staking and restaking options for a diverse array of tokens on the Ethereum network, supported by Arbitrum’s high throughput, low transaction fees, and secure layer 2 scaling infrastructure.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3818\" src=\"https://cryptogem.io/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo_2024-04-11_18-17-36.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"639\" srcset=\"https://cryptogem.io/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo_2024-04-11_18-17-36.jpg 1280w, https://cryptogem.io/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo_2024-04-11_18-17-36-300x150.jpg 300w,