(10, 'RetaFi Become The Next-Gen Liquid Staking Solution', 17, 21, '<h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 38px; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: -0.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><em style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Inspired by the monetary policies of central banks from leading economies such as the US and EU, RetaFi was born with the mission of revolutionizing the financial landscape with Liquid Staking Tokens 2.0 (LST) . So what’s special about this project? Let’s find out with CryptoGem.io</em></p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">What is RetaFi?</strong><br style=\"border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">RetaFi is built on Polygon, which is a Liquid Stake Tokens project inspired by leading central banks. Similar to central banks that manage money supply in traditional finance, RetaFi provides a decentralized solution. Efficient focus for markets to manage assets and provide liquidity.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Now, RetaFi is providing Staking &amp; Restaking services on Blockchains such as Ethereum, BNB Chain, Solana or Polygon.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3796\" src=\"https://cryptogem.io/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo_2024-06-01_17-01-01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"593\" srcset=\"https://cryptogem.io/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo_2024-06-01_17-01-01.jpg 1280w, https://cryptogem.io/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo_2024-06-01_17-01-01-300x139.jpg 300w, https://cryptogem.io/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo_2024-06-01_17-01-01-1024x474.jpg 1024w, https://cryptogem.io/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo_2024-06-01_17-01-01-768x356.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 5px 20px 20px 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br style=\"border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">RetaFi Ecosystem<br style=\"border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"></strong><br style=\"border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Staking Mechanism</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;\">RetaFi’s staking mechanism, powered by EchelonAI, ensures maximum returns and security. Partnering with leading node providers, RetaFi offers NexusStake for efficient collaboration and StakerForge for customizable node deployment. Rewards are distributed transparently, benefiting RCR holders, partners, and the RetaFi Treasury, fostering a decentralized and equitable ecosystem.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-wid