(11, 'Mt.Gox Moves $7B Bitcoin as Part of Repayment Plans, Sparking BTC Price Plunge', 16, 20, '<p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><em style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Nearly 107,000 bitcoin have been moved since early Asian hours on Tuesday, with bitcoin shedding 1.2% on expectations of selling pressure.</em></p><div class=\"article-contentstyles__ArticleSectionWrapper-sc-1lrs40v-1 bWBlCa\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><div id=\"at-content-section-0\" class=\"at-content-section\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"contentstyle__StyledWrapper-sc-g5cdrh-0 gkcZwU composer-content\" data-submodule-name=\"composer-content\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"liststyles__StyledWrapper-sc-13iatdm-0 eksenZ\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"at-list\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><ul class=\" \" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 35px; padding: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; line-height: 2;\"><li style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"typography__StyledTypography-sc-owin6q-0 eycWal\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Over 107,000 BTC, worth around $7 billion, were transferred from Mt. Gox wallets to an unknown address in thirteen transactions, possibly as part of a plan to repay creditors by October 31, 2024.</div></li><li style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"typography__StyledTypography-sc-owin6q-0 eycWal\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">The market reacted bearishly to these movements, with Bitcoin dropping by 1.4% to as low as $67,680 after reaching a high of over $70,000 on Monday.</div></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"common-textstyles__StyledWrapper-sc-18pd49k-0 eSbCkN\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"typography__StyledTypography-sc-owin6q-0 eycWal at-text\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">Wallets belonging to the defunct Bitcoin exchange Mt. Gox transferred over 107,000 bitcoin (BTC), valued at around $7 billion, to an unknown address starting early Asian morning hours on Tuesday.</p></div></div><div class=\"common-textstyles__StyledWrapper-sc-18pd49k-0 eSbCkN\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"typography__StyledTypography-sc-owin6q-0 eycWal at-text\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">Mt. Gox, once the largest bitcoin exchange in the world, closed in 2014 after it was revealed that it had lost hundreds of thousands of bitcoin in a hack. Creditors have since awaited the repayment of their holdings –&nbsp;one that is largely considered&nbsp;to add selling pressure to BTC markets.</p></div></div><div class=\"common-textstyles__StyledWrapper-sc-18pd49k-0 eSbCkN\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"typography__StyledTypography-sc-owin6q-0 eycWal at-text\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">Wallet activity&nbsp;shows the movements were done over thirteen transactions. A likely test transaction worth $3 was made on May 20, and another smaller transaction of $160 was done early Tuesday. The remaining transactions ranged from $1.2 million to $2.2 billion worth of bitcoin.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"article-contentstyles__RailWrapper-sc-1lrs40v-2 bvZgMc at-grid-right extended-rail false false\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"at-rail-wrapper\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"at-rail-content-wrapper\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"article-contentstyles__VertWrapper-sc-1lrs40v-3 fXyeCK\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"display-desktop-block display-tablet-none display-mobile-none \" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"article-contentstyles__ArticleSectionWrapper-sc-1lrs40v-1 bWBlCa\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><div id=\"at-content-section-1\" class=\"at-content-section\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"contentstyle__StyledWrapper-sc-g5cdrh-0 gkcZwU composer-content\" data-submodule-name=\"composer-content\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"common-textstyles__StyledWrapper-sc-18pd49k-0 eSbCkN\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"typography__StyledTypography-sc-owin6q-0 eycWal at-text\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">This is the first movement of assets from Mt. Gox’s cold wallets in over five years and is likely a part of a plan to distribute the assets back to creditors before October 31, 2024.</p></div></div><div class=\"common-textstyles__StyledWrapper-sc-18pd49k-0 eSbCkN\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"typography__StyledTypography-sc-owin6q-0 eycWal at-text\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">All coins have been transferred to a new address “1JbezDVd9VsK9o1Ga9UqLydeuEvhKLAPs6,” CryptoQuant head of research Julio Moreno said in an X post.</p></div><div class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; display: flex; max-width: 550px; width: 550px;\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-0\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" class=\"\" title=\"X Post\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/embed/Tweet.html?dnt=false&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-0&amp;%3D%3D&amp;frame=false&amp;hideCard=false&amp;hideThread=false&amp;id=1795293007908085867&amp;lang=en&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fcryptogem.io%2Fmt-gox-moves-7b-bitcoin-as-part-of-repayment-plans-sparking-btc-price-plunge%2F&amp;sessionId=8adfce398a7e6a0829791f4dd3dcb422855e418e&amp;theme=light&amp;widgetsVersion=2615f7e52b7e0%3A1702314776716&amp;width=550px\" data-tweet-id=\"1795293007908085867\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: static; visibility: visible; width: 550px; height: 672px; display: block; flex-grow: 1;\"></iframe></div><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\"></p></div></div></div><div class=\"common-textstyles__StyledWrapper-sc-18pd49k-0 eSbCkN\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"typography__StyledTypography-sc-owin6q-0 eycWal at-text\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">Alex Thorn, head of research at Galaxy, said in an X post that he expected most of the transferred bitcoin to be held by creditors, instead of being sold on the open market.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">Still, market participants appeared to turn bearish on the movements with bitcoin shedding 1.4% since the start of Asian trading hours. It dropped to as low as $67,680 after a Monday high of over $70,000.</p></div></div></div>', '2018-06-30 19:10:36', '2024-11-04 07:29:03', 1, 'Mt.Gox-Moves-$7B-Bitcoin-as-Part-of-Repayment-Plans,-Sparking-BTC-Price-Plunge', 'b6bbf6f19d8c5718a4563cbc3193e1c5.jpg'),
(12, 'Ethereum?s Price Surge and Potential Setbacks', 17, 21, '<p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Ethereum (ETH), the largest altcoin by market value, had been trading below $2,800 for an extended period before surpassing this key level this week. However, due to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.coin-turk.com/bitcoins-volatility-indicator-signals-a-potential-bull-run/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background 300ms, color 300ms, border-color 300ms; color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">Bitcoin</a>‘s price volatility and the expected decrease in volume over the weekend, it had dropped below this critical region at the time of writing. The ETH rally, which is also crucial for the rise of other altcoins, may not have started yet.</p><h2 id=\"ethereum-eth\" class=\"rb-heading-index-0\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 700; font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 48px; color: rgb(56, 56, 56);\">Ethereum (ETH)</h2><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">In the last 10 days, the&nbsp;<strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">ETH price</strong>&nbsp;has risen by approximately 21%, surpassing $2,800. The altcoin king, buoyed by the excitement of BTC’s new 2024 high of $52,572, was trading below this level at the time of writing. From the perspective of the rise, the average inflow of $450 million into spot Bitcoin ETFs this week is encouraging.</p><div class=\"code-block code-block-3\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"coinzilla\" data-zone=\"C-5664b673dbabde0145\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></div></div><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Moreover, the decisions on&nbsp;<strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">spot ETH ETFs</strong>&nbsp;expected to be finalized in May are anticipated to create expectations and push the price higher. Another significant development boosting the bulls’ motivation is the Dencun update scheduled for March 13. This hard fork will reduce transaction fees for Ethereum layer2 solutions by 90%.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">With ETFs, Dencun, and the&nbsp;<strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Bitcoin halving</strong>, there are many developments supporting ETH’s price rise in the medium term. However, despite all these, ETH is struggling to close above even $2,800. If the weakening altcoin in the ETHBTC pair can reach the January 2024 level (in ETHBTC terms), $3,100 (with the current BTC price) will become possible.</p><div class=\"code-block code-block-1\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"></div><h2 id=\"will-eth-price-fall\" class=\"rb-heading-index-1\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 700; font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 48px; color: rgb(56, 56, 56);\">Will ETH Price Fall?</h2><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">A few metrics need to be examined because the price catalysts mentioned in the first section are not things that will yield immediate results in the short term. The&nbsp;<strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Ether</strong>&nbsp;futures premium rose above the neutral zone on February 10. Normally, trading with a premium of 5-10% is considered normal and neutral. As the premium climbed from $2,300 to $2,800, the futures premium reached 15%, indicating that professional traders benefited from leverage in the rise.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-315884 aligncenter\" src=\"https://coin-turk.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ETH-1-Tahmin.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1183\" height=\"396\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 5px auto; padding: 0px; clear: both; display: block;\"></p><div class=\"code-block code-block-1\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"></div><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Here, we receive the first potential signal of a decline since we see a relaxation area in the neutral zone. On the other hand, the 25% delta skew is a useful indicator to understand the position of professional investors. If this is above 7%, it indicates an expectation of a decline, and the opposite is indicated around -7%. This is at the lowest level in three months, and there is a significant area like the futures premium that indicates a weakening of excitement.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-315885 aligncenter\" src=\"https://coin-turk.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ETH-Tahmin-2.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1168\" height=\"395\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 5px auto; padding: 0px; clear: both; display: block;\"></p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Analysts pointing to the possibility of a correction in the&nbsp;<strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">BTC</strong>&nbsp;price have been more vocal these days, so it wouldn’t be surprising to see rapid sales begin. On the other hand, Bloomberg ETF analysts’ probability of approval for spot Ethereum ETFs (decision date May 23) is at 70%.</p>', '2018-06-30 19:11:44', '2024-11-04 07:29:50', 1, 'Ethereum’s-Price-Surge-and-Potential-Setbacks', 'cbc5b4f10fe7c62d1d91938ffd31a4b5.jpg');
