(18, 'Bitcoin set for supply shock as ETF buys surge and halving nears', 11, 13, '<p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Bitcoin could be on the cusp of a major supply shock thanks to two key events: the upcoming halving in April and a recent surge in demand from newly approved Bitcoin exchange-traded funds (ETFs).</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">The Bitcoin halving, which occurs every four years, cuts the block reward miners receive in half. This slashes the new supply of Bitcoin entering the market, tightening overall availability. With the next halving just months away, supply is set to drop drastically even as demand rises.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">That demand is coming primarily from institutional investors via Bitcoin ETFs. Top ETF providers like BlackRock have bought over $4.3 billion worth of Bitcoin through these funds in just seven days, according to Bloomberg analyst&nbsp;Eric Balchunas. With more than 112,000 BTC accumulated quickly, these ETFs highlight the growth in appetite for Bitcoin exposure among institutions.</p><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"500\" data-dnt=\"true\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-color: rgb(226, 226, 226); border-image: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 33px 33px 18px; quotes: none; font-size: 18px; font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">LATEST: The Great GBTC Gouge hit record -$640m on Monday, the Nine did their best to offset but fell short w/ a $553m haul. ROLLING NET FLOWS still healthy at +$1b but ongoing battle. The Nine now have a 20% share vs GBTC. Volume also remains very high for new launches in 2nd wk&nbsp;pic.twitter.com/ng0BU8mi6L</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">— Eric Balchunas (@EricBalchunas)&nbsp;January 23, 2024</p></blockquote><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">This combination of surging demand and shrinking supply sets the stage for a supply shock. On-chain&nbsp;data&nbsp;from Blockware’s Mitchell Askew shows over 70% of Bitcoin hasn’t moved in over a year, indicating limited sell-side liquidity.</p><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"500\" data-dnt=\"true\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-color: rgb(226, 226, 226); border-image: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(245, 245, 245); margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 33px 33px 18px; quotes: none; font-size: 18px; font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">Despite the launch of&nbsp;#Bitcoin&nbsp;ETFs presenting an opportunity to “sell the news”, most HODL’ers (unsurprisingly) have not done so.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">A record % of the BTC supply remains untouched.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">The new demand from ETFs, that will come slowly, not all at once, will be met with incredible…&nbsp;pic.twitter.com/WEbMREayuH</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;\">— Mitchell&nbsp;<img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\"??\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/svg/1f1fa-1f1f8.svg\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 17.9861px; border-width: initial !important; border-style: none !important; vertical-align: -0.1em !important; background: none !important; margin: 0px 0.07em !important; padding: 0px !important; height: 1em !important; display: inline !important; box-shadow: none !important;\"><img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\"?\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/svg/1f680.svg\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 17.9861px; border-width: initial !important; border-style: none !important; vertical-align: -0.1em !important; background: none !important; margin: 0px 0.07em !important; padding: 0px !important; height: 1em !important; display: inline !important; box-shadow: none !important;\">&nbsp;(@MitchellHODL)&nbsp;January 18, 2024</p></blockquote><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Askew suggests that the fresh demand from ETFs will be absorbed by “incredible supply-side illiquidity” over time. This may lead to intensified competition for limited available Bitcoin, potentially sending its price upward.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">However, whether an actual shock materializes depends on many factors. These include potential price fluctuations, changing regulations, and variations in overall demand.</p><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(230, 230, 230); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(99, 99, 99); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Bitcoin’s price saw stagnation during the first week of spot ETF trading. At press time, Bitcoin is hovering around $39,500, down over 7% over the last seven days, according to&nbsp;data&nbsp;from CoinGecko.</p>', '2024-11-04 07:42:09', NULL, 1, 'Bitcoin-set-for-supply-shock-as-ETF-buys-surge-and-halving-nears', '4d884e892bb7631f12b5cb89f9dcc16a.jpg'),
(19, 'As SOL drops 5% in 24 hours, can Solana NFTs save the day?', 11, 13, '<ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\">Solana’s NFT trade count and trade volume in USD spiked.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\">SOL was down by over 6%, and indicators looked bearish.</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"https://ambcrypto.com/predictions/solana-price-prediction\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" style=\"opacity: 1; transition: 0.3s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 140, 69); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Solana’s [SOL]</span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;NFT ecosystem flourished over the last seven days as several key metrics surged. This happened at a time when its native token lost over 5% of its value in 24 hours.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">However, will the blockchain’s achievements in the NFT ecosystem have any indirect positive impact on SOL’s price?</span></p><h4 style=\"backface-visibility: hidden; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\">Solana NFTs boom!</span></h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">AMBCrypto’s look at CryptoSlam’s</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cryptoslam.io/blockchains/solana?headerPeriod=7d&amp;timeFrame=day\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" style=\"opacity: 1; transition: 0.3s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 140, 69); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">data</span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;revealed that Solana’s NFT ecosystem witnessed growth on multiple fronts over the last week. For instance, its NFT sales volume spiked by more than 40%.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><br></span><span style=\"text-align: center;\">A similar increasing trend was also noted in terms of the number of sellers and buyers, as they grew by over 71% and 62%, respectively.</span></p><div id=\"attachment_365298\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; max-width: 100%; width: 1067px;\"><a href=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL.png.webp\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"opacity: 1; transition: 0.3s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 140, 69); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-365298\" class=\"wp-image-365298 size-full entered lazyloaded\" src=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1057\" height=\"237\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL.png.webp 1057w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL-300x67.png.webp 300w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL-1024x230.png.webp 1024w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL-768x172.png.webp 768w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1057px) 100vw, 1057px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL.png.webp\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1057px) 100vw, 1057px\" srcset=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL.png.webp 1057w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL-300x67.png.webp 300w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL-1024x230.png.webp 1024w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/CRYPTOSLAM-SOL-768x172.png.webp 768w\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; backface-visibility: hidden; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-365298\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Source: CRYPTOSLAM</p></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Other datasets also painted a similar picture of growth. AMBCrypto’s analysis of Santiment’s data pointed out that Solana’s total NFT trade counts increased last week.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">SOL’s NFT trade volume in USD also spiked substantially, reflecting more activity.&nbsp;</span></p><div id=\"attachment_365299\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; max-width: 100%; width: 3850px;\"><a href=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Solana-SOL-13.50.24-22-Jan-2024.png.webp\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"opacity: 1; transition: 0.3s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 140, 69); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-365299\" class=\"wp-image-365299 size-full entered lazyloaded\" src=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Solana-SOL-13.50.24-22-Jan-2024.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"3840\" height=\"1300\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Solana-SOL-13.50.24-22-Jan-2024.png.webp 2560w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Solana-SOL-13.50.24-22-Jan-2024-300x102.png.webp 300w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Solana-SOL-13.50.24-22-Jan-2024-1024x347.png.webp 1024w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Solana-SOL-13.50.24-22-Jan-2024-768x260.png.webp 768w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01