in: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 140, 69); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-365300\" class=\"wp-image-365300 size-full entered lazyloaded\" src=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1837\" height=\"521\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL.png.webp 1837w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL-300x85.png.webp 300w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL-1024x290.png.webp 1024w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL-768x218.png.webp 768w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL-1536x436.png.webp 1536w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1837px) 100vw, 1837px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL.png.webp\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1837px) 100vw, 1837px\" srcset=\"https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL.png.webp 1837w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL-300x85.png.webp 300w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL-1024x290.png.webp 1024w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL-768x218.png.webp 768w,https://ambcrypto.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dune-SOL-1536x436.png.webp 1536w\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; backface-visibility: hidden; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-365300\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Source: Dune</p></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">To check which NFT collections performed the best on Solana, AMBCrypto took a look at DappRadar’s</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dappradar.com/rankings/nft/collections/chain/solana?range=week\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" style=\"opacity: 1; transition: 0.3s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 140, 69); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">data</span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">We found that CryptoUndeads, STEPN, and Open Solmap were the top three NFT collections on the blockchain in the past seven days.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Aside from these, Frogana and Mad Lads also made it to the top five on the same list.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Another piece of optimistic news was recently revealed for</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ambcrypto.com/solana-surges-by-5-in-24-hours-whats-next-rally-or-slump/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" style=\"opacity: 1; transition: 0.3s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(217, 140, 69); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">SOL</span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">’s NFT ecosystem. Nearly 16,000 Solana Saga mobiles have been activated to date.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Since mobile plays a major role in promoting SOL NFTs, this development might have a positive effect on the ecosystem soon.</span></p><div class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; max-width: 550px; width: 550px;\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-0\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" class=\"\" title=\"X Post\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/embed/Tweet.html?creatorScreenName=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDiDipayan&amp;dnt=true&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-0&amp;%3D%3D&amp;frame=false&amp;hideCard=false&amp;hideThread=false&amp;id=1748861429317316811&amp;lang=en&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fambcrypto.com%2Fas-sol-drops-5-in-24-hours-can-solana-nfts-save-the-day%2F&amp;sessionId=9fad991c837c3a6abe2c52ebc4d94da202601b45&amp;siteScreenName=CryptoAmb&amp;theme=light&amp;widgetsVersion=2615f7e52b7e0%3A1702314776716&amp;width=550px\" data-tweet-id=\"1748861429317316811\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; vertical-align: baseline; position: static; visibility: visible; width: 550px; height: 778px; display: block; flex-grow: 1;\"></iframe></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25p